gobblin.broker

Class SharedResourcesBrokerImpl<S extends ScopeType<S>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.broker.SharedResourcesBrokerImpl<S>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SharedResourcesBroker<S>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class SharedResourcesBrokerImpl<S extends ScopeType<S>>
extends Object
implements SharedResourcesBroker<S>
    An implementation of SharedResourcesBroker using a DefaultBrokerCache for storing shared objects. Instances of this broker must be created as follows: 
      SharedResourcesBrokerImpl rootBroker = SharedResourcesBrokerFactory.createDefaultTopLevelBroker(myConfig);
  SharedResourcesBrokerImpl scopeBroker = topBroker.newSubscopedBuilder(scope, "scopeId").build();
